cdata.name: Sociall
cdata.desc:
Sociallis a social network. All data and uploads will exist on the blockchain instead of centralized servers.Sociallis a platform that allows users to communicate with friends and family while providing security and privacy. By decentralizing and encrypting all data and uploads,Sociallhopes to eliminate all invasion of privacy that large corporations are currently performing. End-to-end message encryption ensures only the user and the person communicating with the user, can read what is sent, and nobody in between, not even Sociall.

The network will Sociallits very own native cryptocurrency to be used for all purchases, calledSociall. SCL can be used to buy goods and services from other users, purchase ad spaces from the integrated ad platform, donate to crowdfunding campaigns, and much more.
